summary: Hey! This is my custom customization of the ENB files. I hope you enjoy it. Be warned though, it makes nights really dark and days really beautiful. Flames and bright lights looks nice too, creating lens flares. Well. Hope you enjoy it!
descriptionHtml:
This is my ENB customization of the enbseries file. Adding lens flares to bright lights infront of you. Making days brighter and more beautiful. Making nights and dark areas even darker so a torch is infact needed! Adds bump mapping to walls and other. Bloom. All that good stuff.

Supported with any realistic lighting modification. As any ENB file. 

FPS WARNING
Might drop fps quite low determining on you CPU. Should be fine though ;]

Made by FO3ghoul
